com.amazonaws.mobileconnectors.s3.transfermanager

Interface ObjectMetadataProvider

  • Deprecated. 
    The Transfer Manager is now deprecated in favor of the TransferUtility

    @Deprecated
public interface ObjectMetadataProvider
    This is the callback interface which is used by TransferManager.uploadDirectory and TransferManager.uploadFileList. The callback is invoked for each file that is uploaded by TransferManager and given an opportunity to specify the metadata for each file.
